column5: XONE indestructible at 8 100k trades in 15 mins and XONE did not lose a beat This is a whole different character 6 months ago if 100k shares had to trade in 15 mins it would have lost like 50 cents There is an invisible hand at 8 Spring is getting tighter and tighter every week and this time XONE is showing it has the tensile strength to hold at 8 and catapult when the moment arrives
